Adadin kamuwa da cutar korona (COVID-19) da ya karu a cikin Tarayyar Turai/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da Burtaniya, 1 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020
Adadin mutanen da suka kamu da cutar korona (COVID-19) ya nuna irin wannan halin tsakanin kasashen Tarayyar Turai / Turai da Kasuwancin da ke tsakanin Birtaniya wanda ke tabbatar da cewa, duk da cewa matsalar COVID-19 tana da matakan daban-daban a cikin ƙasashe daban-daban, tana ƙaruwa da sauri a duk faɗin duniya.
A cewar abin da ya faru a Italiya, ƙasashe, asibitoci da dakunan shan magani masu tsanani suna bukatar su kara kasancewa a shirye don karuwar yawan masu cutar COVID-19 da ke bukatar magani, musamman na gaggawa.
A ranar 31 ga Disamba, 2019, an gano wasu mutane da ke fama da cutar ta huhu da ba a san dalilinta ba a Wuhan, lardin Hubei, China.
A ranar 9 ga Janairu, 2020, Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Rigakafin Cutar Sin ta ba da rahoton cewa cutar ta kamu da cutar coronavirus wacce ba a san asalinta ba wanda yanzu aka sani da cutar ta shan numfashi mai tsanani coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Tun daga wannan lokacin, an kira cutar ta SARS-CoV-2 cutar coronavirus (COVID-19).
Binciken ya nuna cewa kusan kashi 80% na mutanen da ke da cutar COVID-19 suna da ƙananan cututtuka, wato, kamuwa da cutar numfashi tare da ko ba tare da cutar kumburi ba, kuma yawancin sun warke.
A cikin kusan kashi 14 cikin dari, COVID-19 ya zama babban cuta mai bukatar kwancewa kuma kashi 6 cikin dari na mutane sun kamu da cutar mai tsanani da ke bukatar magani mai tsanani.
Kashi 4 cikin 100 na marasa lafiya da aka kwantar da su a gado saboda COVID-19 sun mutu.
A cikin wannan binciken, mun bincika karuwar kamuwa da COVID-19 a kowace ƙasa ta Tarayyar Turai/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai (EU/EEA) da Turai (UK) kuma mun kwatanta shi da lardin Hubei, China.
Muna kuma kwatanta yawan adadin masu kamuwa da COVID-19 a halin yanzu a cikin EU/EEA da UK da Italiya a lokacin 31 Janairu15 Maris 2020.
Masu kamuwa da COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da Burtaniya
Bayan China, COVID-19 ya bazu zuwa wasu yankuna kuma halin COVID-19 ya bazu a wasu sassan duniya bayan wannan ƙasar.
A ranar 11 ga Maris, 2020, Babban Jami'in Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ya bayyana COVID-19 a matsayin annoba ta duniya.
A cikin fitowar Eurosurveillance 2020 na 5 ga Maris, Spiteri da abokan aikinsa sun yi tsokaci kan farkon kamuwa da COVID-19 a Turai bisa ga bayanin WHO.
A cikin EU/EEA, an gano kamuwa da cutar ta farko a Faransa a ranar 24 ga Janairu 2020 lokacin da mutanen suka bar Wuhan, lardin Hubei, China.
A ranar 15 ga Maris, 2020, an gano kamuwa da COVID-19 a duk ƙasashen EU / EEA 30 da Burtaniya, daga cikin wannan tsakanin 31 ga Disamba 2019 zuwa ranar da aka shigar, akwai masu kamuwa da cutar 39,768 da mutuwar 1,727, tare da marasa lafiya 17,750 da mutuwar 1,441 daga Italiya kadai.
Yawan masu kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 da kuma yawan mutanen da suka kamu da COVID-19 suna ƙaruwa
A Cibiyar Tarayyar Turai don Rigakafin Cututtuka da Kulawa (ECDC), an sabunta lambobin kamuwa da COVID-19 a kowace ƙasa a duniya, daga kafofin watsa labarai na hukumomi kamar Ma'aikatar Lafiya ta Duniya, ofisoshin WHO na Lafiya na Duniya da kuma lambobin sadarwa, kowace rana da karfe 2:00 na safe.
An yi amfani da wannan bayanan ne don nazarin COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da Burtaniya, kuma a kwatanta su da na Italiya.
A matsayin ƙididdigar yawan masu cutar COVID-19 da ake bi da su, mun ƙididdige adadin mutanen da aka gano COVID-19 a cikin kwanaki 14, a kowace ƙasa ta EU/EEA da Burtaniya, a lokacin 1 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris 2020.
Mun kuma nuna adadin masu kamuwa da cutar a kowace ƙasa yayin da ake ci gaba da karuwa a ranar 15 ga Maris, 2020 da ƙarfe 2:00 na safe idan aka kwatanta da a Italiya a ranar 31 ga Janairu, 15 ga Maris.
Halin COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da Burtaniya
Yawan adadin mutanen da suka kamu da cutar COVID-19 da aka gano a cikin kwanaki 14 a cikin EU/EEA da Burtaniya gaba ɗaya ya biyo bayan na lardin Hubei (China) (Hoto 1).
A cikin EU/EEA da Birtaniya gaba ɗaya, adadin mutanen da suka kamu da COVID-19 ya fara ƙaruwa a ranar 21 ga Fabrairu kuma ya ƙaru sosai a ranar 28 ga Fabrairu 2020 (Yuli).
Wannan ya faru ne saboda karuwar da ake samu daga Italiya, amma kamar sauran kasashen EU/EEA da Birtaniya sun samu karuwar adadin mutanen da suka kamu da COVID-19 (Covid-19).
Hoto na 2 ya nuna yawan adadin kamuwa da COVID-19, a cikin EU/EEA da Burtaniya idan aka kwatanta da na Italiya a lokacin 31 Janairu15 Maris 2020.
Ya nuna cewa, a ranar 15 ga watan Agusta da ƙarfe 2:00 na safe, ƙasashen EU/EEA da sauran ƙasashen 15 na Burtaniya sun sami adadin adadin masu kamuwa da cutar da ya yi daidai da wanda aka samu a Italiya makonni 3 da suka gabata ko ƙasa da haka.
Binciken ya nuna cewa adadin masu kamuwa da COVID-19 yana ƙaruwa da sauri a cikin EU/EEA da Burtaniya.
Bayanai na yawan mutanen da suka kamu da COVID-19 sun nuna cewa cutar tana ƙaruwa a cikin ƙasa da ƙasa.
Wannan ya ci gaba da kasancewa haka ko da yake ƙasashe suna da tsarin kiwon lafiya a matakai daban-daban, da kuma ka'idoji daban-daban don yanke shawara ko mutum yana da cutar da kuma ka'idoji daban-daban don yanke shawara game da mutanen da za a gwada don tabbatar da COVID-19, gami da ƙara yawan mutanen da za a gwada.
A farkon watan Maris na 2020, likitoci a yankunan da aka yi wa rauni a Italiya sun bayyana halin da ake ciki cewa kashi 10% na masu cutar COVID-19 suna buƙatar gaggawa kuma labarai sun nuna cewa asibitoci da dakunan gaggawa a waɗannan yankuna sun cika.
Bayanai na COVID-19 da ke kwance a asibiti da/ko a cikin dakin kulawa mai tsanani da ke rufe matakin EU/EEA sun kai kashi 6% zuwa 1% kawai, (ba a bayyana wannan bayanin ba).
Maimakon haka, ya kamata a tattara waɗannan a cikin tsari mai kyau bisa ga bayanan da aka nuna game da yawan marasa lafiya da suka mutu.
Wani bincike da aka yi a shekara ta 2010-11 ya nuna bambanci tsakanin yawan wuraren da ake yin jinya da kuma wuraren da ake yin jinya a Turai, inda a Jamus ake samun gado 29.2 a kan kowane mutum 100,000, a Portugal kuma akwai gado 4.2 a kan kowane mutum 100,000.
Wannan yana nufin cewa akwai ƙasashe da ke da mafi yawan ko kuma mafi ƙarancin adadin wuraren kiwon lafiya fiye da Italiya (wannan yana nufin gado 12.5 na lafiya da rashin lafiya ga kowane mutum 100,000 a shekara ta 201011).
Sakamakon da ke tattare da cika kayan aikin kiwon lafiya, dangane da kwatancen marasa lafiya na COVID-19 a cikin gado a kowace ƙasa ta EU / EEA da Burtaniya da kuma ƙalubalen da ake samu yayin da buƙatar wuraren shakatawa na kiwon lafiya ya ƙaru da kashi 90%, an bayyana a cikin rahoton na shida na ECDC na saurin kimanta haɗarin COVID-19.
Tun da yake har yanzu akwai ci gaba da samun marasa lafiya a wasu sassan EU/EEA da Birtaniya, kuma asibitoci da dakunan kula da lafiya suna kula da mutane a wasu sassan da aka sani, za a samu bayanai game da marasa lafiya da dakunan kula da lafiya ta hanyar Nomenclature of territorial units for statistics 2 (NUTS-2).
Labaran da aka samu a Italiya da kuma kasashen waje sun nuna cewa cutar COVID-19COVID-19 tana karuwa da sauri a cikin EU/EEA da Burtaniya.
Saboda haka, asibitoci da wuraren kula da gaggawa suna bukatar su shirya don yaduwar SARS-CoV-2 a cikin al'umma da kuma karuwar yawan mutanen da ke fama da COVID-19 da ke bukatar magani, musamman ma na gaggawa, kamar yadda yake a yankunan da aka hana a Italiya.
Kamar yadda aka nuna a cikin binciken ECDC na gaggawa, shiri na gaggawa yana da muhimmanci wajen hana yaduwar SARS-COV-2, yayin da yake motsawa daga hana yaduwa zuwa warkewa, domin ƙaruwar gaggawa a cikin adadin marasa lafiya da ake tsammani na iya hana hukumomi da asibitoci samun isasshen lokaci don ganewa, amincewa da aiwatar da hanyoyin da za a bi idan ba a aiwatar da su a gaba ba.
Binciken gaggawa na gaggawa ya nuna hanyoyin kiwon lafiya da za su magance matsalar.
Akwai ƙananan ƙasashe da ke da ikon haɓaka ƙarfin su don rage yaduwar SARS-CoV-2 da kuma rage matsin lamba akan kiwon lafiya.
Idan hakan bai yi nasara ba, ana sa ran cewa za a matsa wa tsarin kiwon lafiya a sauran ƙasashen EU/EEA saboda yawan marasa lafiya da ke bukatar karin magani a cikin kwanaki ko makonni masu zuwa.
Cutar Coronavirus ta 2019 (COVID-19), wadda ke haifar da cutar ta SARS (SARS) coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2), ta kashe mutane sama da 3,000 kuma sama da mutane 80,000 sun kamu da cutar a China da sauran wurare a duniya, wanda ya haifar da bala'i ga al'umma.
Kamar yadda yake da cutar SARS-CoV, wadda ta haifar da SARS a dubban mutane a shekara ta 2003, SARS-CoV-2 na iya kamuwa da cutar ta hanyar bugun jini kuma yana haifar da alamun bayyanar cututtuka iri ɗaya.
Koyaya, COVID-19 ba ta da ƙarfi kamar SARS kuma tana kashe mutane kaɗan amma ana ɗaukar ta fiye da yadda take shafar manya da maza fiye da matasa da mata.
A cikin amsa ga yawancin labarai game da wannan cuta, wannan shafin yana nufin ya nuna cikakken bincike game da sakamakon haɗari.
Za mu tattauna abubuwa na asali game da cututtuka, abin da ke jawo su, ƙwayoyin cuta, bincike, magani, tsinkaya, da kuma guje musu.
Ko da yake akwai tambayoyi da yawa da za a amsa, muna ganin cewa wannan binciken zai taimaka mana mu fahimci kuma mu magance wannan cuta mai tsanani da ke damun mutane.
Bikin bazara na 25 ga Janairu, 2020 ya zama abin tunawa ga Sinawa waɗanda aka nemi su zauna a gidajensu na hutu da makonni masu zuwa saboda barkewar cutar da ba a san ta ba.
Wannan kwayar cutar ta kama da cutar coronavirus (CoV) wacce ta haifar da cutar ta shan numfashi mai tsanani (SARS) a shekara ta 2003; saboda haka, Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ta sake kiran ta SARS-CoV-2 a ranar 11 ga Fabrairu, 2020, kuma ta sake kiran cutar ta COVID-19 (COVID-19).
Wannan cuta ta fara ne a birnin Wuhan da ke kasar Sin, kuma ba da daɗewa ba ta bazu a dukan ƙasar da kuma wasu ƙasashe 50 a faɗin duniya.
A ranar 2 ga watan Agusta, 2020, cutar ta riga ta haifar da mutane sama da 80,000 da aka tabbatar da cewa suna da COVID-19, fiye da 40,000 sun warke kuma fiye da 3,000 sun mutu.
WHO ta yi gargadin cewa COVID-19 shine makiyin mutum na 1 kuma yana iya zama mafi haɗari fiye da ta'addanci.
A cewar PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/), a cikin ƙasa da watanni biyu, an buga shafuka sama da 200 game da COVID-19 wanda ya haɗa da cutar, cuta, abin da ke haifar da cutar, gwaji da magani tun daga rahoton farko a ranar 7 ga Janairu, 2020 wanda ya gano asalin cutar ta rarrabe daga masu cutar daban-daban.
Wannan binciken ya yi ne don ya yi daidai da binciken da aka yi a wannan sabon filin wasa da ke ci gaba da ci gaba sosai.
A farkon, za mu gwada COVID-19 da SARS da wani cuta da ake kira CoV, ciwon huhu na Gabas ta Tsakiya (MERS, wanda ya barke a shekara ta 2012).
Za mu kuma tattauna abin da muka koya game da yadda za mu guji kamuwa da cutar da kuma wasu tambayoyi masu muhimmanci da ba a amsa su ba.
Ana ganin cewa CoVs ba su da lahani ga mutane, domin sun fi kusan kashi 15 cikin 100 na yawan mura 4.
A cikin wannan karni, mun sami nau'ikan CoVs biyu masu haɗari ga mutane, wato SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV, waɗanda suka haifar da cutar ta farko a China a 2003 da Saudi Arabia a 2012, kuma nan da nan suka bazu zuwa wasu ƙasashe tare da cutar da ta kashe mutane da yawa.
Saboda haka, COVID-19 da ke faruwa a yanzu ita ce cutar ta uku ta CoV da ta faru a tarihin ɗan adam.
Kamar yadda aka nuna a Hoton. Hoton.1,1, an fara sanar da masu fama da cutar zazzabin cizon sauro a Wuhan a ranar 31 ga Disamba, 2019 ga Hukumar Lafiya ta Kasa ta kasar Sin.
Bayan kwana bakwai, an fitar da rahoton CoV.
A ranar 15 ga Janairu, 2020, an yi rahoton kamuwa da cutar ta farko daga Wuhan.
A wannan lokacin, cutar ta yi ta yaduwa cikin sauri a garuruwan da ke kusa da ita, da kuma ƙasashe.
A ranar 20 ga Janairu, an yi magana game da cutar ta likitoci, wanda ya nuna cewa mutane za su iya kamuwa da cutar ta wajen yin kishi da mutane.
A ranar 23 ga Janairu, an rufe birnin Wuhan kuma an dakatar da zirga-zirgar jiragen sama a duk faɗin duniya.
A ranar 24 ga Janairu, binciken farko na asibiti na cutar ya nuna cewa, daga cikin mutane 41 da aka tabbatar da cutar, 21 ne kawai suka kai tsaye zuwa kasuwar kifin Wuhan inda ake zaton cutar ta fara ne daga wani dabba da ba a san shi ba.
A ranar 30 ga Janairu, WHO ta bayyana cewa cutar ta zama gaggawa a duniya.
