A ranar 11 ga Fabrairu, 2020, binciken da aka gudanar a wurare daban-daban na mutane 8,866 waɗanda aka tabbatar da cewa suna da COVID-19 4,021 sun ba da sabon bayanin cutar ta kyauta (https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/UlBi-HX_rHPXa1qHA2bhdA).
