Matsalar COVID-19 guda uku da suka fi tsanani ita ce jima'i (maza), shekaru (≥60), da kuma ciwon sukari.
Kwayar CoVs ta kasance cikin manyan kwayoyin cuta masu ƙwayoyin cuta da ke kewaye da su kuma suna da RNA mai laushi ɗaya.
Ana iya raba shi zuwa nau'i hudu (genera), wato alpha, beta, gamma, da delta, wanda alpha- da beta-CoVs sun san su da cutarwa ga mutane.
(S) glycoprotein yana da alaƙa da ƙwayoyin angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 (ACE2) da dipeptidyl peptidase 4 (DPP4) a cikin SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV, a cikin wannan haɗin, sai ƙwayoyin fatsun biyu su haɗu.
Ana aika kwayar RNA ta kwayar zuwa cikin kwayar; bayan an sake kwayar kwayar kwayar, kwayar RNA ta haɗa da glycoproteins da nucleocapsid sunadarai don samar da kwayar cutar, wanda ke haɗuwa da kwayar cutar ta jini don samar da kwayar cutar.
An bayyana asalin SARS-CoV-2 a ranar 10 ga Janairu, 2020.
An gano SARS-CoV-2 a matsayin sabon nau'in beta-CoV wanda ya dace da kwayoyin halitta 99.98% na samfurori 10 da aka gwada an samo su daga wurin da cutar ta fara kasancewa, Huanan Seafood Market a Wuhan.
SARS-CoV-2 ya fi kama da SARS-CoV a cikin kwayoyin halitta fiye da MERS-CoV.
Ta hanyar amfani da na'urori masu haske, an gano kwayoyin SARS-CoV-2 a cikin sassan hanyar iska mai iska.
An gano cewa enzymes ACE2 suna kare SARS-CoV-2 tare da SARS-CoV.
A maimakon haka, furotin S na SARS-CoV-2 yana da alaƙa da enzymes na ACE2 amma ba shi da ƙarfi kamar SARS-CoV, wanda ya dace da gaskiyar cewa SARS-CoV-2 yana da haɗari a cikin mutane idan aka kwatanta da SARS-CoV.
SARS-CoV-2 kuma yana iya samar da wani ƙaramin furotin da ba a taɓa gani ba wanda za a iya kira orf3b da kuma furotin da aka saki wanda za a iya kira orf8.
SARS-CoV-2 orf3b na iya zama mai cutarwa ga mutane kuma yana hana IFNβ bayyana; amma, orf8 ba shi da wani abu mai tasiri.
A ranar 18 ga Fabrairu, 2020, Zhou, da abokan aikinsa, sun nuna cikakken tsarin cryo-EM na enzyme ACE2 a ƙuduri na 2.9 Å a cikin amino acid B0AT1.
Sun gano cewa wannan haɗin, wanda ya ƙunshi kwayoyin cuta biyu, ya kasance a cikin kwayoyin cuta kuma haɗin ACE2-B0AT1 zai iya haɗa sunadarai na S, wanda ke nuna tabbacin gano CoV da wanda ya kama shi.
B0AT1 na iya zama manufa don magani saboda gwajin maganin cutar SARS-CoV-2.
Tushen da ke Ƙarfafa
An san cewa SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV sun samo asali ne daga kwayoyin halitta kuma sun isa ga mutane ta hanyar kwayoyin halitta da raƙuma, a cikin wannan yanayin.
Idan aka kwatanta SARS-CoV-2 da sauran CoVs, ana ganin cewa ƙwayar cuta tana da tasiri sosai wajen watsa SARS-CoV-2 saboda wannan ƙwayar cuta ta yi daidai da kashi 96% na sauran CoVs biyu masu kama da SARS waɗanda kuma suna cikin ƙwayar cuta kamar bat-SL-CoVZX45 da bat-SL-CoVZX21.
Amma, ba a san ainihin dabbar da ta kai ga mutane ba, kuma ba a san hanyar da ta bi ba.
Ji da abokan aikinsa sun yi imanin cewa macizai sun yi amfani da ƙwayar cuta ta hanyar yin amfani da kwayoyin S don su kai ga mutane.
A cewar wani bincike, masu bincike a Guangzhou, China, sun nuna cewa ƙwari (pangolin) - wani dabba mai ƙarancin hanci, mai cin kwayoyin cuta wanda ake amfani da shi a cikin maganin gargajiya na kasar Sin - zai iya watsa SARS-CoV-2 zuwa mutane bisa ga daidaitattun kwayoyin halitta na 99% na CoV da aka gano a cikin hanci da SARS-CoV-2.
Amma, bambancin kashi ɗaya cikin ɗari tsakanin kwayoyin halitta biyu ya kasance da yawa; saboda haka, ba a samu cikakken tabbaci ba (Fig. 33).
Ba a san yawancin cututtukan SARS-CoV-2 ba tukuna.
Kwayar cutar SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV na iya kasancewa a cikin gilashi na tsawon sa'o'i 48 a bushe da kwanaki 5 a zafin jiki na 20 °C da 40%-50%.
SARS-CoV-2 na iya zama irin wannan cutar.
An gano cewa SARS-CoV-2 ba ya haɗuwa da hasken rana (rays ultraviolet) da zafin jiki na 56 °C na tsawon minti 30; aƙalla kashi 75%, kwayoyin da ke dauke da chlorine, peracetic acid, kalifofi, da sauran kwayoyin cuta, amma ba chlorhexidine ba, suna iya kashe kwayar cutar.
Dukan mutane gabaɗaya ba su da rigakafi ga SARS-CoV-2 kuma saboda haka suna iya kamuwa da cutar.
A halin yanzu, babu wani bincike da aka yi game da cutar SARS-CoV-2.
Saboda haka, za mu iya dogara ne kawai ga binciken da aka yi a baya game da CoVs, musamman SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV (Figure (Figure 4).4).
A yawancin lokaci, idan kwayar cuta ta kai wa dabba mai motsi hari, ana fara gano tsarin ƙwayar cuta ta hanyar ƙwayoyin cuta masu ganewa (PRRs) wanda ya haɗa da masu karɓar lectin irin na C-type), mai karɓar Toll-like (TLR), mai karɓar NOD (NLR), da mai karɓar RIG-I (RLR).
Ta hanyar hanyoyi daban-daban, kwayar cutar ta haifar da gina jiki, ci gaban ƙwayoyin dendritic, da kuma samar da interferons na I-type interferons (IFNs) waɗanda ke hana yaduwar kwayar cutar kuma suna ƙara ƙarfin macrophage don yaƙi da kwayar cutar.
A maimakon haka, furotin N na SARS-CoV na iya taimakawa wajen tsalle daga ciwon daji.
Nan da nan, ƙwayar ƙwayar cuta ta daidaitawa ta shiga cikin yaƙin da ake yi da ƙwayoyin cuta.
Kwayoyin T lymphocytes da ke ɗauke da CD4+ da CD8+ suna da muhimmiyar rawa wajen yaƙi da ƙwayoyin cuta.
Kwayoyin T na CD4+ suna sa kwayoyin B su yi aiki da su wajen yin yaki da ƙwayoyin cuta, kuma CD8+ T cells suna kashe waɗanda ba su da cutar.
Kwayoyin T helper suna samar da cytokines masu ƙonewa don taimakawa wajen hana rigakafi.
A maimakon haka, ƙwayar CoV tana iya hana T cell yin aiki ta wajen sa T cells su mutu.
Ƙwayoyin rigakafi na jiki da suka haɗa da furotin kamar C3a da C5a da kuma rigakafi suna da amfani wajen yaki da ƙwayar cuta.
Alal misali, an cire kwayoyin rigakafi daga mai haƙuri da ya warke kuma ya kamu da cutar MERS-CoV.
A wani ɓangare kuma, yawan ƙwayar cuta yana haifar da ƙwayoyin cuta masu yawa da ke haifar da lalacewar huhu da sauran sassan jiki, wasu kuma suna sa sassan jiki da yawa su kasa yin aiki kuma a wasu lokatai su mutu.
Kwayar cutar SARS-CoV-2, wadda aka samu a cikin mutane na farko, ta fi rinjayar tsofaffi da ke fama da wasu cututtuka da kuma mata masu ciki.
A bayyane yake cewa mutane da suke da cututtuka dabam-dabam ko kuma ƙarancin ƙwayar cuta suna da zarafin kamuwa da cutar fiye da wasu.
Lokacin da cutar SARS-CoV-2 ke ɗaukar bayyanar cututtuka shine kwanaki 1-14, yawanci kwanaki 3-7 bisa ga binciken da aka yi akan mutane 425 na farko a Wuhan.
Amma, wani bincike da aka yi a kan mutane 1,099 ya nuna cewa a matsakaita, ƙwayar cuta tana ɗaukan kwanaki uku kafin ta nuna alamun cutar kuma a cikin kwanaki 0 zuwa 24.
Wani sabon bincike da aka ambata ɗazu ya nuna cewa yana da kwanaki 4.8 (3.0-7.2) bisa ga masu haƙuri 8,866.
Yana da muhimmanci masana kiwon lafiya su tsara kwanakin keɓewa bisa ga lokacin da cutar ta nuna alamun cutar, don su hana mutane da suke da cutar da ba su da alamun cutar da za su iya kamuwa da wasu.
A yawancin lokaci, ana bukatar a killace mutanen da suke da cutar ko kuma waɗanda suke da ita har kwana 14.
Shin ana bukatar a ƙara tsawon lokacin da ake killace mutane zuwa kwanaki 24?
Cutar zazzabi tana zama babban alamar COVID-19 na farko, wanda ba za a iya bi da shi ba tare da wata alama ko alamomi kamar rashin ƙarfi, rashin numfashi, ciwon tsoka, ciwon hanci, ciwon kai, ƙuƙwalwa a wuyansa, ƙuƙwalwa a hanci, ciwon kirji, gudu, numfashi, da numfashi.
Wasu marasa lafiya sun sami matsala wajen numfashi da kuma/ko kuma rashin numfashi a cikin jini bayan mako guda bayan sun kamu da cutar.
A cikin yanayi mafi tsanani, marasa lafiya sun sami matsala a cikin huhu, rashin jini, rashin ƙwayar cuta, da kuma cututtukan coagulopathy.
Masu fama da zazzabi da kuma/ko alamun cutar ta gaggawa, ko da ba su da wata cuta a huhu, suna bukatar a gwada su kafin su gano ko suna da kwayar cutar.
Binciken da aka yi a watan Disamba na 2019 ya nuna cewa kashi 98% na alamun sun kasance a cikin kumburi, kashi 76% a cikin kumburi, kashi 55% a cikin wahalar numfashi, da kashi 3% a cikin rashin ƙarfi; kashi 8% na marasa lafiya suna buƙatar na'urorin numfashi.
An gano irin wannan binciken a cikin bincike guda biyu da aka yi da marasa lafiya da suka mutu a cikin iyali ɗaya da kuma waɗanda suka mutu a cikin wani mutum da ba su da alamun cutar.
A kwatanci, binciken da aka yi a cikin mutane a shekara ta 2012 ya nuna cewa masu cutar MERS-CoV sun sami zazzabi (98%), ƙarancin ƙarancin jini (47%), da kuma wahalar shan numfashi (55%) a matsayin manyan alamun su.
Duk da haka, kashi 80% na su na bukatar na'urorin taimako na jini, musamman ga marasa lafiya na COVID-19 kuma wannan ya yi daidai da gaskiyar cewa MERS ya fi cutar COVID-19 haɗari.
An kuma lura da ɓarna (26%) da kuma ɓarna a cikin wuya (21%) a cikin masu cutar MERS.
A cikin masu cutar SARS, an nuna cewa zazzabi (99%-100%), ƙarancin zazzabi (29%-75%), wahalar numfashi (40%-42%), gudu (20-25%), da kuma ciwon hanci (13-25%) sune manyan alamun bayyanar cututtuka kuma ana buƙatar kayan aikin numfashi a cikin 14%-20% na marasa lafiya.
A ranar 14 ga Fabrairu, adadin mutanen da suka mutu daga COVID-19 ya kai kashi 2 cikin dari na adadin masu kamuwa da cutar a duniya, wanda ya kai 66,576.
A wannan kwatancen, adadin mutanen da suka mutu daga cutar SARS a watan Nuwamba na shekara ta 2002 ya kai kashi 10 cikin 100 na adadin masu kamuwa da cutar 8,096.
A cikin cutar ta MERS, a cikin wani bincike da aka yi a watan Yuni na shekara ta 2012, kashi 37 cikin ɗari na mutanen da suka mutu sun kai 2,494 da aka tabbatar da cutar.
Binciken da aka yi a baya ya nuna cewa R0 na SARS-CoV-2 ya kasance mafi girma a 6.47 yayin da ƙimar amincewa (CI) ya kasance kashi 95% a 5.71-7.23, yayin da R0 na SARS-CoV ya kasance tsakanin 2 zuwa 4 kawai.
Ana kwatanta SARS-CoV-2 da MERS-CoV da SARA-CoV dangane da alamun bayyanar cututtukan, ƙwayoyin cuta, da R0 a cikin Labari na 1.1.
Wadannan kididdigar sun nuna cewa SARS-CoV-2 yana da mafi yawan yaduwar cutar fiye da MERS-CoV da SARS-CoV, amma ba su da haɗari kamar sauran biyu.
Saboda haka, yana da wuyar rage cutar SARS-CoV-2 fiye da na MERS-CoV da SARS-CoV.
Mutane da suke da ciwon daji suna zama a gida ɗaya ko kuma a taro ɗaya ko kuma a mota ɗaya kamar jirgin ruwa.
Masu kamuwa da cutar ta Wuhan sun yi tafiya daga ko sun zauna a Wuhan ko wasu wurare da cutar ta kamu ko kuma sun kasance tare da mutanen da ke dauke da cutar ko kuma sun kamu da cutar makonni biyu kafin kamuwa da cutar.
Amma, an bayyana cewa mutane za su iya kamuwa da cutar amma ba su nuna alamun cutar ba har tsawon makonni biyu kuma waɗanda suka warke kuma aka kwantar da su daga asibiti za su iya sake kamuwa da cutar, wanda ke nuna cewa za a bukaci karin lokaci na keɓewa.
A cikin marasa lafiya, yawan adadin ƙwayoyin fari na jini (musamman na lymphocytes) da ke cikin jini yana ƙaruwa ko kuma ya ragu a farkon lokaci.
Alal misali, an gano lymphopenia tare da ƙididdigar ƙwayoyin fari na jini &lt; 4×109/L ciki har da ƙididdigar lymphocyte &lt; 1×109/L, da aspartate aminotransferase da kuma viremia a cikin mutane 1,099 da suka kamu da COVID-19.
An samu adadin enzymes da myoglobin a cikin jini na wasu marasa lafiya, kuma sun samu sunadarai masu aiki na C da kuma sedimentation na erythrocyte a cikin jini na yawancin marasa lafiya.
A cikin marasa lafiya masu tsanani, adadin D-dimer, wanda shi ne samfurin lalata fibrin a cikin jini, ya ƙaru, kuma adadin lymphocytes ya ragu.
Akwai wasu cututtukan kirji a cikin yawancin marasa lafiya na COVID-19 kuma wannan yana tare da cututtukan huhu (ɓawon ƙasa na biyu ko kuma ƙasa mai haske).
A yawancin lokaci, marasa lafiya suna fama da ciwon kumburi, da kuma bugun huhu da kuma ciwon huhu (ARDS).
Idan ARDS ta faru, ana gina ruwa da yawa, kuma nama yana rufe raunuka da ke haifar da matsala a cikin iska.
Pneumocytes na I da II (nau'in I da nau'in II) suna rage yawan surfactant kuma suna ƙara matsa lamba a saman, wanda hakan ke rage ƙarfin huhu don faɗaɗa kuma yana ƙara yawan rashin nasarar huhu.
Saboda haka, sakamakon gwajin ƙirjin da ya fi muni sau da yawa ya yi daidai da yanayin rashin lafiya mafi muni.
A ranar 18 ga Fabrairu, 2020, binciken farko na COVID-19 a cikin gwaji ya nuna haɓakar ƙwayoyin cuta, haɓakar hyaline, haɓakar fata, da ƙwayoyin syncytial multinucleated a cikin huhu na mai haƙuri da ya mutu daga cutar, wanda ya yi kama da nazarin marasa lafiya da ke da cutar da ARDS kuma yayi kama da na SARS da MERS.
Gano RNA na SARS-CoV-2 ta hanyar juyawa-transcriptase polymerase chain reaction (RT-PCR) an yi amfani da shi azaman babban aikin bincike na COVID-19.
Amma, saboda an gano cewa mutane da yawa ba su da cutar kuma suna da ita, wanda zai iya haifar da cutar, an fara amfani da siginar cutar a cikin gwaji (ba tare da dogara ga RT-PCR kawai) a China ba a ranar 13 ga Fabrairu, 2020.
Haka kuma, an yi gwajin SARS.
Saboda haka, haɗa tarihin kamuwa da cuta, alamun cututtuka, gwajin gwaji, da kuma yin hoto yana da muhimmanci kuma ya dace a yi domin a samu ƙwarewar gano cutar.
A ranar 14 ga Fabrairu, 2020, ƙungiyar Feng Zhang ta bayyana wani tsari na amfani da fasaha ta SHERLOCK mai tushen CRISPR don gano SARS-CoV-2, wanda ke gano SARS-CoV-2 RNA a cikin 20 × 10-18 mol/L zuwa 200 × 10-18 mol/L (kwafin 10-100 a kowace microliter ana gwadawa) ta amfani da matattarar ruwa a cikin ƙasa da minti uku ba tare da buƙatar gwaji mai yawa ba.
Ana sa ran wannan sabuwar hanyar za ta taimaka wajen gano ko an yi amfani da ita a cikin samfurin da ake gwadawa.
Saboda rashin sanin cutar ta CoV da ba a sani ba, likitoci sun fi dacewa su kula da masu cutar COVID-19, yayin da suke gwada magungunan da aka yi amfani da su ko kuma aka nuna a baya don magance wasu ƙwayoyin cuta na CoV kamar SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV da kuma wasu cututtukan cuta (Rubes (Rubes).2).
Wannan magani na zamani yana da amfani wajen magance cututtukan cuta, yana rage yawan ciwon daji, steroids, jini (plasma) daga masu warkewa, maganin gargajiya na kasar Sin, da kuma ta'aziyya.
An kuma yi amfani da jini na mutanen da suka warke don magani.
Kamfanonin ƙwayoyi suna aiki tuƙuru don samar da rigakafi da kuma maganin rigakafin cutar.
SARS-CoV-2 ya fi yawaita a cikin huhu da farko kuma yana iya kaiwa ga sauran sassan da ke da ACE2, ciki har da tsarin gastrointestinal da kuma fitsari.
Duk da haka, matsalar rashin jinin jini ita ce mafi yawan cututtuka da kuma sanadin mutuwa.
Saboda haka, kayan aikin iska suna da muhimmanci wajen magance matsalolin da ke sa rai da kuma ceton rai, kuma hakan ya haɗa da abubuwa kamar maganin oxygen na gaba ɗaya, oxygen mai gudana sosai, iska mai ba da izini, da kuma iska mai amfani da inji mai amfani da ke sa rai bisa ga yawan cutar.
Masu fama da matsalar numfashi suna bukatar taimako ta hanyar maganin oxygenation na membrane extracorporeal (ECMO), wanda shi ne tsarin da ake amfani da shi wajen magance rashin numfashi da ke haifar da mutuwa.
Sauran abubuwa, kula da matakan electrolyte, hanawa da kuma kula da wasu ƙwayoyin cuta masu cutar da ke iya yaduwa, da kuma kula da muhimman sassan jiki suna da muhimmanci ga masu cutar SARS-CoV-2.
An san cewa hadari na cytokine daga tsutsa yana haifar da matsanancin amsawar tsarin rigakafi a cikin masu cutar SARS da MERS.
Cytokine storm wani abu ne na jiki wanda ke haifar da wani abu mai mahimmanci don samar da cytokines daban-daban ciki har da TNFα, IL-1β, IL-2, IL-6, IFNα, IFNβ, IFNγ, da MCP-1.
Waɗannan kwayoyin suna sa tsarin rigakafin jiki ya samar da kwayoyin da ke sa ARDS da sauran kwayoyin jikinmu su kasa aiki.
Rage yawan ciwon daji yana da muhimmanci wajen magance hadari na cytokine, musamman a cikin marasa lafiya masu tsanani.
Ana amfani da corticosteroids da tocilizumab, irin su anti-IL6 monoclonal antibody, don magance hadari na cytokine.
Sauran hanyoyin da za a iya amfani da su wajen rage cutar ta jini sun hada da daidaita tsarin garkuwar jiki na T cell-directed immune response; hana IFN-γ, IL-1, da TNF; hana JAK; blinatumomab; suppressor of cytokine signaling 4; da kuma masu hana HDAC.
Ana amfani da steroids, wanda ake amfani da su don rage kumburi, a cikin maganin SARS don rage tasirin gina jiki.
Duk da haka, amfani da steroids a cikin adadi mai yawa bai taimaka wajen rage haɗarin kamuwa da cutar huhu a cikin marasa lafiya na SARS da COVID-19.
A wasu lokatai, suna iya haifar da sakamako masu tsanani, musamman ƙwayoyin jijiya, wanda zai iya shafar sakamakon da ake tsammani.
Duk da haka, an ba da shawarar yin amfani da corticosteroids a cikin marasa lafiya masu cutar COVID-19 masu tsanani a cikin ƙananan allurai.
A lokacin da ake rubuta wannan shafin, babu wani magani da aka tabbatar da cewa zai iya magance cutar.
Amma, an gano cewa shan remdesivir a cikin jini, irin wannan analog na nucleotide, yana da tasiri a kan wani mai cutar COVID-19 a Amurka.
Remdesivir sabon maganin ƙwayoyin cuta ne da Gilead ta yi amfani da shi a dā don magance cututtukan Ebola da Marlburg.
Daga baya, an gano cewa remdesivir zai iya magance wasu ƙwayoyin cuta masu ƙwayoyin RNA guda ɗaya, ciki har da MERS da SARS.
Bisa ga wannan, Gilead ta ba kasar Sin wannan magani don gwaji a kan mutane da ke dauke da SARS-CoV-2, kuma sakamakon yana jiran mutane da yawa.
Bugu da ƙari, ana ba da shawarar baricitinb, interferon-α, lopinavir/ritonavir, da ribavirin a matsayin magani mai kyau don magance cututtukan numfashi masu tsanani.
Ƙarƙashin zuciya, numfashi, cizon sauro, cutar hanta, da wasu matsaloli masu tsanani na iya faruwa idan an haɗa lopinavir/ritonavir da wasu magunguna.
Ana bukatar a yi la'akari da yadda wannan magani yake da kuma sauran magunguna da ake amfani da su a cikin marasa lafiya.
Plasma daga marasa lafiya da suka warke da kuma antibody
Ana yin amfani da jini daga waɗanda aka yi amfani da shi wajen warkar da wasu marasa lafiya da suke da irin wannan cuta ko kuma don a ceci rayayyun mutane daga kamuwa da cutar.
Hakika, waɗanda suka warke daga cutar suna da ƙwayoyin rigakafi da yawa a cikin jininsu.
Antibodies wani nau'i ne na maganin rigakafi da kwayoyin B suke yi don su yi yaki da ƙwayoyin cuta da kuma wasu abubuwa da ba su da kyau a jikin mutum kuma su yi amfani da kwayoyin da ke cikin kwayoyin don su hana su yin aiki.
Bisa ga wannan, an cire plasma daga jinin ƙungiyar masu tsira daga COVID-19 zuwa cikin marasa lafiya 10 masu tsanani.
A cikin sa'o'i 24, yanayin sun inganta, kuma an rage yawan kamuwa da cutar, kuma an rage yawan iska da jini.
Maimakon haka, dole ne a kasance da tabbaci da kuma fahimi don a yi amfani da duk wani tsari da za a yi amfani da shi ga mutane da yawa kafin a ci gaba da yin amfani da wannan hanyar.
Bugu da ƙari, saboda sakamakon shan magani, dole ne a fara bincika sakamakon da ke tattare da jini.
Alal misali, ƙwayoyin rigakafi suna iya sa ciwon ya ƙaru sosai kuma hakan ya haifar da cutar cytokine, wadda ke haifar da guba mai tsanani.
Ana yawan samun ƙarancin kwayoyin rigakafi a cikin jini, kuma ana bukatar jini sosai don a warkar da marasa lafiya.
Yana da wuya a samar da rigakafi da sauri don magance matsalar cutar ta duniya.
Saboda haka, za a iya rarrabe kwayoyin B daga waɗanda suka warke kuma a yi bincike don a gano tsarin ƙwayoyin cuta na ƙwayoyin cuta ko kuma a yi bincike don a gano ƙwayoyin cuta na ƙwayoyin cuta na babban ƙwayar cuta.
Ta wannan hanyar, za mu iya ƙara yawan ƙwayar ƙwayar ƙwayar cuta.
An yi amfani da TCM wajen magance cututtuka da yawa a kasar Sin tun dubbai na shekaru.
Maimakon haka, aikinsa ya dogara ne a kan haɗa abubuwa daban-daban a cikin magunguna waɗanda ke canzawa bisa ga gano cutar bisa ga ka'idar TCM.
Ba a san ko kuma ba a san ainihin abubuwan da suke da amfani ba domin yana da wuya a iya tantance su.
A halin yanzu, saboda babu wata sanarwa da za ta magance COVID-19, TCM na ɗaya daga cikin magunguna da aka fi amfani da su wajen magance marasa lafiya da ke da ƙananan alamun cutar ko waɗanda suka warke a matakai kaɗan.
Alal misali, an gano cewa takalma Shu Feng Jie Du da Lian Hua Qing Wen sun yi tasiri sosai wajen magance COVID-19.
Yawancin masu kamuwa da cutar sun tsira daga COVID-19 a larduna da yawa na kasar Sin yayin da aka yi musu magani tare da TCM a cikin yankuna 87% na masu kamuwa da cutar, ciki har da Gansu (63.7%), Ningxia (50%), da Hunan (50%), da kuma lardin Hubei, wanda ya yi amfani da TCM a cikin kusan 30% na masu kamuwa da COVID-19, inda samun nasarar ya kasance mafi ƙaranci (13%).
