Kwayar cutar korona ta samo asali ne daga dabba
Canjin kwayoyin halitta ya haifar da canjin kwayar cutar corona (CoVs) da kuma yanayin rayuwar dabbobi, ciki har da mutane, na dubban shekaru.
Kafin 2003, an san cewa kwayar cuta ta CoVs (HCoVs) tana haifar da ƙananan cututtuka, kamar mura ta yau da kullun.
Fitowar cutar ta SARS da kuma cutar ta MERS ta Gabas ta Tsakiya sun kawo canji ga yadda cutar HCoV za ta iya zama mai cutarwa da kisa.
Fitar da SARS-CoV-2 a tsakiyar China a ƙarshen 2019 ya dawo da CoVs a cikin fitsari kuma ya ba mu mamaki da yadda ake sarrafa shi a cikin sauri kuma ba shi da tasiri sosai idan aka kwatanta da SARS-CoV.
HCoVs na fitowa ne daga dabbobi kuma gano asalin HCoVs na dabba yana da amfani sosai.
Yawancin kwayoyin HCoVs suna fitowa ne daga ƙwayoyin cuta kuma ba su da cutar.
An san wasu daga cikin kwayoyin HCoVs na farko da suka fara rarraba kansu kafin su shiga cikin mutane.
Sanin dabbobi da ke kamuwa da cuta yana taimaka wajen magance cututtuka da ke kamuwa da mutane.
Yin nazarin dangantakar dabbobi da ke cikin CoV zai iya taimaka wajen sanin haɗarin CoV a cikin mutane.
A cikin wannan binciken, za mu taƙaita binciken da aka samu na HCoVs bakwai, sannan mu yi la'akari da tarihin gano su da asalin su a cikin dabbobi da kuma yadda suka yada tsakanin dabbobi daban-daban.
A cikin wannan, za mu nuna kamanceceniya da bambance-bambance tsakanin HCoVs daban-daban ta hanyar nazarin juyin halitta da kuma sake haɗuwa da kwayoyin halitta.
An yi magana ne game da cutar COVID-19 a wannan yanayin.
An kuma tattauna abubuwan da ke sa dabbobi da ke da ƙwayoyin cuta su canja jiki da kuma yadda za su iya canja yanayin da za su iya sa a sami cutar.
Kwayar cutar corona (CoVs) ta kasance cikin dangin Coronaviridae, wanda ya ƙunshi rukuni na ƙwayoyin cuta da ke kewaye da ƙwayoyin cuta, kowannensu positive-sensed, kuma yana da RNA na layi ɗaya.
Wannan kwayar cuta tana da babban genom na 26 zuwa 32 kilobases a cikin RNA kwayar cuta kuma an kira ta CoVs saboda nau'in ta mai kama da kambi lokacin da aka kiyaye ta a cikin kayan yisti.
A cikin gine-gine, ƙwayoyin cuta na CoVs suna da ƙwayoyin halitta da ba a rarraba su ba kuma suna tare.
Kimanin kashi biyu bisa uku na kwayoyin halitta suna da manyan kwayoyin halitta guda biyu (ORF1a da ORF1b), waɗanda suke samar da pp1a da pp1ab replicase polyproteins.
Daga baya, an yi amfani da kwayoyin da aka yi amfani da su wajen samar da furotin 16 da ake kira nsp1~16.
Ragowar kwayoyin halitta sun ƙunshi ORFs a kan sunadarai masu gina jiki, ciki har da spike (S), envelope (E), membrane (M) da nucleoprotein (N).
Ana kuma haɗa ƙwayoyin cuta da yawa na musamman zuwa jerin CoVs.
Dangane da bambancin ƙwayoyin cuta, ana rarraba CoVs zuwa manyan nau'ikan (alpha-CoV, beta-CoV, gamma-CoV da delta-CoV), wanda nau'in beta-CoV shine mafi yawan HCoVs kuma an rarraba shi zuwa layi huɗu (A, B, C da D).
Binciken da aka samu daga binciken ya nuna cewa ƙwayoyin cuta ne tushen mafi yawan alpha-CoVs da beta-CoVs, kuma tsuntsaye ne tushen mafi yawan gamma-CoVs da delta-CoVs.
A cikin dubban shekaru, CoVs sun fito ne daga dabbobi kuma sun zama tushen cututtukan mutane.
Har zuwa yanzu, an san nau'ikan CoV guda bakwai na mutum (HCoVs).
A cikin waɗannan HCoV-229E da HCoV-NL63 suna cikin nau'in alpha-CoVs.
Sauran beta-CoVs guda biyar sun hada da HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1, coronavirus na cututtukan numfashi mai tsanani (SARS-CoV), coronavirus na cututtukan numfashi na Gabas ta Tsakiya (MERS-CoV) da SARS-CoV-2.
HCoV-229E, HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1 da HCoV-NL63 suna haifar da ƙananan cututtuka, kamar mura na yau da kullun da / ko kumburi.
Akasin haka, SARS-CoV, MERS-CoV da SARS-CoV-2 da aka gano kwanan nan suna da ƙarancin cutar, suna shafar ƙananan ƙwayar cuta a cikin mafi yawan marasa lafiya kuma akwai yiwuwar haɗarin cutar ta numfashi mai tsanani (ARDS) da bayyanar cututtukan huhu.
An gano nau'in HCoV-229E na farko, B814, a cikin kwayoyin cutar mura a tsakiyar shekarun 1960.
Tun daga wannan lokacin, an sami ƙarin bincike mai zurfi game da HCoV-229E da HCoV-OC43, dukansu suna haifar da alamun rashin lafiya na kai tsaye.
A gaskiya ma, an yi imani da cewa kamuwa da cutar HCoVs gaba ɗaya ba ta da haɗari har sai da barkewar SARS.
Cutar SARS ta barke a shekara ta 2003 kuma ta kasance ɗaya daga cikin bala'o'i mafi muni a tarihin 'yan kwanan nan, inda ta kama mutane fiye da 8,000, kusan kashi 10% na waɗanda ke da begen mutuwa.
Shekaru goma bayan haka, cutar ta hanyar numfashi ta Gabas ta Tsakiya (MERS) ta jawo wani annoba a Gabas ta Tsakiya da ba ta yadu da sauran ƙasashe ba.
2019 novel HCoV (2019-nCoV), wanda daga baya aka sani da SARS-CoV-2, ya haifar da cutar coronavirus ta 2019 (COVID-19), wanda ya kashe mutane sama da 3,120 kuma ya kama mutane sama da 91,000 a ranar 3 ga Maris 2020.
Jahannama tana busawa kuma dole ne duniya ta shirya don cutar ta SARS-CoV-2 ta duniya.
Dukkanin cututtukan HCoVs guda bakwai sun fito ne daga ƙwayoyin cuta, ƙusa ko dabbobi masu kiwo.
Akwai shaidu da yawa da suka nuna cewa dukkanin HCoVs sun samo asali ne daga kwayoyin halitta, inda kwayoyin halitta ba su da cutar amma suna da tsarin halittu daban-daban.
Cutar COVID-19 ta haifar da manyan kalubale a fannin kiwon lafiya, kimiyya, zamantakewa da kuma zamantakewa a China da kuma duniya.
Bin diddigin asalin HCoVs a cikin dabbobi yana ba mu damar fahimtar tarihin, wanda ke hana kamuwa da cuta daga wasu dabbobi zuwa wasu.
Wannan kuma na iya taimakawa wajen sauƙaƙe aikin gano wani dabba mai daukar hoto na SARS-CoV-2 daga dabba zuwa mutum, wanda ke da muhimmiyar mahimmanci wajen hana yanayin yaduwar.
A cikin wannan binciken, mun gano asalin HCoVs a cikin dabbobi, yadda suka yadu a cikin dabbobi daban-daban da kuma irin cututtukan da suke haifarwa.
Musamman, muna nunawa da kuma tattauna batun cewa cutar HCoVs ba ta haifar da cutar daga dabba ba amma ta zama mai haɗari idan ta wuce zuwa wani dabba.
Mun kuma bincika yadda kwayar HCoV ke canzawa yayin da ake samun karuwa kuma sau da yawa yana rage haɗarin kamuwa da cutar.
Sakamakon barkewar cutar SARS-CoV-2 na yanzu ana magana a kai a wannan yanayin.
An gano cewa dabba tana da ƙwayar cuta ta CoVs tun daga shekara ta 1930.
Kafin a gano cutar HCoV-229E mai suna B814 a cikin ƙwayoyin cuta na marasa lafiya na mura na yau da kullun, yawancin ƙwayoyin cuta na CoVs sun samo asali ne daga dabbobi masu cutar, gami da tsutsotsi, ƙwari, shanu, aladu, kabeji da karnuka.
A cikin ƙarni da suka gabata, an gano nau'ikan HCoV guda bakwai.
Labarin da aka yi na gano HCoV a cikin jerinsa (Figure 1) zai koya mana darasi.
An gano HCoV-229E na farko a cikin ƙwayar cuta na marasa lafiya da suka sami rauni a cikin ƙashin ƙafar ƙafar a shekara ta 1966, kuma an gano shi yana sarrafawa a cikin ƙwayoyin cuta na huhu na WI-38.
Marasa lafiya da ke dauke da cutar HCoV-229E sun nuna alamun cutar mura, ciki har da ciwon kai, yin tawaye, ƙwanƙwasa a wuyansa, da kuma zazzabin cizon sauro da kuma zubar da jini a cikin marasa lafiya da suka kai kashi 10 zuwa 20%.
Daga baya a shekara ta 1967, an gano HCoV-OC43 a cikin tsarin sarrafa kwayoyin halitta sannan kuma a cikin tsarin wucewa ta hanyar kwakwalwa a cikin kwakwalwar da ke shan nono.
Alamomin likitanci na HCoV-OC43 sun yi kama da na HCoV-229E, wanda ya bambanta da na sauran ƙwayoyin cuta kamar su ƙwayar cutar mura A da rhinoviruses.
HCoV-229E da HCoV-OC43 duka suna tafiya a ko'ina cikin duniya, kuma suna tafiya sosai a lokacin hunturu a cikin yanayin sanyi.
A gaba ɗaya, waɗannan ƙwayoyin cuta biyu suna nuna alamun cutar a cikin ƙasa da mako guda, kuma hakan yana biyo bayan tsawon mako biyu.
Bisa ga binciken da aka yi a kan masu ba da gudummawa, mutanen da suka kamu da cutar HCoV-229E sun kamu da cutar mura ta al'ada.
Wasu marasa lafiya da ba su da ƙarancin ƙwayar cuta sun ji rauni sosai a ƙananan ƙashin ƙashin ƙugu.
SARS, wanda aka fi sani da atypical pneumonia, shi ne farkon wanda aka rubuta a cikin cutar ta duniya ta HCoV a tarihin ɗan adam kuma ta SARS-CoV, kwayar cutar HCoV ta uku da aka gano.
An fara samun cutar SARS a ƙarshen shekara ta 2002 a lardin Guangdong na kasar Sin.
Cutar SARS ta kama mutane 8,096 da aka sani kuma ta kashe mutane 774, ta yada zuwa ƙasashe da nahiyoyi da yawa.
Baya ga sanannun cututtukan da aka sani, an kiyasta cewa kowane mai haƙuri zai iya kamuwa da wasu mutane biyu, a cikin kwanaki 4 zuwa 7 ana nuna alamun cutar yayin da ƙaruwar ƙwayar cuta ta mutum (ƙaruwar ƙwayar cuta) ta faru a ranar 10 na cutar.
Masu kamuwa da SARS-CoV suna fama da ciwon jijiyoyi, kai, zazzabi, kumburi da kuma ciwon baya, sannan kuma suna fuskantar wahalar numfashi, hawaye da kuma samun ruwa daga huhu.
Lymphopenia, gwajin aikin hanta, da kuma karuwar creatine kinase sune wasu cututtukan SARS da aka lura da su a cikin gwajin gwaji.
Ana samun cutar ta huhu (diffuse alveolar damage), yaduwar kwayoyin epithelial da kuma karuwar cutar ta macrophages a cikin masu cutar SARS.
Kimanin kashi 20-30 cikin ɗari na marasa lafiya suna bukatar ƙarin magani da kuma na'urorin da ke taimakawa wajen zubar da jini.
Baya ga ƙananan ƙwayar cuta, wasu sassan ciki har da hanji, hanta da ƙwayar cuta suna iya yin rauni a cikin waɗannan yanayi masu tsanani, sau da yawa tare da hadari na cytokine, wanda ke haifar da mutuwa musamman a cikin marasa lafiya da ƙananan ƙwayar cuta.
An gano wannan kwayar cutar ne a cikin dabba da aka yi amfani da ita a cikin huhu na ɗan'uwa da aka fara gano cutar da ya kai Hong Kong daga birnin Guangzhou.
Tun daga wannan lokacin, an yi ƙoƙari sosai wajen gano HCoV.
An gano HCoV-NL63 a cikin jariri mai watanni 7 daga Netherlands a ƙarshen 2004.
Da farko, ana ganin cewa ana iya samun cututtukan da ke sa a cikin yara da manya da kuma marasa lafiya da ke fama da cututtukan da ke sa a cikin ƙashin ƙugu.
Cutar coryza, cutar kumburi, zazzabi, da kuma kumburi na huhu (bronchiolitis) suna da yawa a cikin cututtukan da HCoV-NL63 ke haifarwa.
Wani bincike ya nuna cewa an gano wannan kwayar cutar a cikin gwajin hanci na wani yaro mai wata takwas da ke fama da cutar kumburi a Netherlands.
Ko da yake an gano shi a ƙasar Netherlands, amma a gaskiya ya bazu a dukan duniya.
An kiyasta cewa HCoV-NL63 ya haifar da kusan kashi 4.7% na kamuwa da cutar da ke tattare da kamuwa da cuta ta yau da kullun, wanda ya fi faruwa a farkon bazara, bazara da hunturu.
HCoV-NL63 yana da alaƙa da ƙwayar cuta (obstructive laryngitis, ko croup).
A wannan shekarar, an gano HCoV-HKU1 a cikin wani mutum mai shekaru 71 da aka sanya masa a kan gado saboda cutar kumburi da kuma ciwon huhu a Hong Kong.
Baya ga cutar kumburi da kuma kumburi, an gano HCoV-HKU1 yana da alaƙa da matsanancin cutar asma.
Kamar HCoV-NL63, HCoV-229E da HCoV-OC43, an gano HCoV-HKU1 a duniya, yana haifar da cututtukan da suka shafi shan iska mai rauni.
Dukkanin waɗannan nau'ikan HCoVs guda huɗu sun saba da mutane kuma gabaɗaya ba a tsammanin za su iya haifar da mummunan cututtuka, kodayake akwai haɗari ga wasu dalilai da ba a sani ba kamar yanayin da ba a samu ba na HCoV-NL63, wanda aka nuna kwanan nan ya haifar da mummunan rauni a yankin ƙananan ƙafar ƙasar Sin.
A gaba ɗaya, HCoVs suna samun damar yin tafiya da kyau a cikin mutane, kuma suna zama marasa haɗari.
An fara gano cutar MERS-CoV a cikin 2012 a cikin huhu na wani mutum mai shekaru 60 da haihuwa wanda ya kamu da cutar mura mai tsanani da kuma rashin samun jini a Saudi Arabia.
Ko da yake duk wani mutum da aka samu ya fito ne daga Gabas ta Tsakiya, an samu karin wadanda suka kamu da cutar daga kasashen waje a kasashen Turai da Tunisia.
A shekara ta 2015, an sake samun cutar a Koriya ta Kudu kuma an samu mutane 186 da suka kamu da ita.
Halin likita na MERS yana kama da SARS, wanda ke dauke da cutar ta kumburi mai tsanani (progressive acute pneumonia).
Ba kamar SARS ba, yawancin masu cutar MERS sun sami rashin ƙarfi na hanji, wanda a halin yanzu shine MERS kaɗai a cikin cututtukan da HCoV ke haifarwa.
Fiye da kashi 30 cikin dari na marasa lafiya suna fama da matsaloli na lalata, kamar su rashin ƙarfi da kuma numfashi.
A ranar 14 ga Fabrairu, 2020, fiye da marasa lafiya 2500 da aka tabbatar da gwaji sun sami ƙimar mutuwa mai girma na kashi 34.4%, wanda ya sa MERS-CoV ɗayan ƙwayoyin cuta mafi haɗari a cikin mutane.
A tsakiyar zuwa ƙarshen Disamba 2019, an gano wasu masu fama da zazzabin cizon sauro da aka sani da cutar SARS-CoV-2 a Wuhan, lardin Hubei, China.
Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta bayyana halin da ake ciki na cutar ta ƙananan ƙwayoyin cuta da SARS-CoV-2 ke haifarwa a matsayin Gaggawa na Lafiya ta Jama'a na Kula da Lafiya ta Duniya (Public Health Emergency of International Concern) kuma ana kiran cutar COVID-19.
A ranar 3 ga watan Agusta, 2020, an sami kamuwa da cutar 90,053 a duniya, wanda ya kai kashi 3.4% na mutuwar.
A cikin kasar Sin, kashi 4.2 cikin 100 ne ke mutuwa a birnin Hubei, amma a kasashen waje kashi 1.2 ne ke mutuwa.
SARS-CoV-2 yana haifar da mummunan rauni ga jijiyoyin jiki kamar SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV, ta hanyar ƙwayoyin cuta, hawaye da wahalar numfashi.
Wasu marasa lafiya ma suna iya yin ba'a.
Rashin ƙarfi yana ɗaya daga cikin alamun da suka fi tsanani kuma zai iya ƙara tsanani da sauri kuma ya jawo matsala a hanyar jirgin ƙasa.
Ko da yake SARS-CoV da SARS-CoV-2 suna da kamanceceniya sosai saboda yawan kamanceceniya (high nucleotide sequence homology) na kashi 82%, suna zuwa daga rassan daban-daban na itacen asalin (phylogenetic tree).
SARS-CoV-2 yana da ƙarancin cutar amma yana da yawa idan aka kwatanta da SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV.
An gano wasu marasa lafiya da ba su da alamun cutar SARS-CoV-2 kuma suna iya taimakawa wajen hanzarta yaduwar ta a duniya.
Idan aka kwatanta wannan haɗuwa da SARS-CoV-2 da sauran HCoVs shida, za a iya gano bambance-bambance da yawa da suka dace.
Na farko, lokaci da alamun cutar suka bayyana da kuma tsawon lokacin da cutar HCoV ke kamuwa da ita suna da kamanceceniya.
A wannan yanayin, SARS-CoV-2 yana bin tsarin hali na HCoVs shida.
Na biyu, haɗuwa da alamun COVID-19 yana tsakanin SARS-CoV da HCoVs huɗu (watau HCoV-229E, HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1 da HCoV-NL63).
A gefe guda, mutum mai dauke da SARS-CoV-2 yana da alamun bayyanar cututtuka da aka fi gani a cikin mutumin da ke dauke da HCoVs, wanda ya ƙunshi alamun da ba a san su ba, ba su da tsanani ko kuma ba su da alamun bayyanar cututtuka.
A gefe guda kuma, ƙananan masu kamuwa da COVID-19 a cikin lokaci na iya zama kamar waɗanda ke da SARS-CoV, koda kuwa ƙananan adadin su.
Na uku, yaduwar SARS-CoV-2 ta kuma nuna yanayin da ke cikin yaduwar HCoVs da SARS-CoV.
A gefe guda, yaduwar SARS-CoV-2 tana da ƙarfi kamar HCoVs.
A gefe guda kuma, babu tabbaci ko cutar SARS-CoV-2 za ta ragu bayan ta shiga cikin mutane kamar yadda ta faru da SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV.
A ƙarshe, kamar sauran HCoVs, SARS-CoV-2 na iya bayyana a cikin samfurin cutar.
Ko mutum zai iya kamuwa da SARS-CoV-2 a cikin yanayin da ya dace kamar SARS-CoV a wasu lokuta dole ne a tabbatar da shi a cikin binciken da za a yi a gaba.
Yana da mahimmanci a lura da ko SARS-CoV-2 na iya kasancewa yana da wani lokaci na aiki kamar HCoVs.
