Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ta bayyana COVID-19 a matsayin matsalar duniya
A ranar Laraba, Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ta bayyana barkewar cutar COVID-19  a matsayin cuta da ke haifar da kwayar cutar coronavirus SARS-CoV-2  a matsayin babbar matsalar duniya.
Ko da yake kalmar nan "ƙaddamar da cuta a dukan duniya" tana nufin yadda cutar ta yadu, ba yadda wasu cututtuka suke da haɗari ba, WHO ta ce gwamnatoci masu kyau su yi aiki don su kawar da cutar:
"Dukan duniya za ta iya canja yadda wannan matsalar ta yadu.
Idan duniya ta yi amfani da shi, za ta yi bincike, ta bi da ita, ta ware ta, ta kula da ita, kuma ta yi wa mutane gargaɗi a kan wannan batu", in ji Babban Jami'in Hukumar Kula da Lafiya ta Duniya, Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus.
"Mun damu sosai game da yadda wannan cuta take yaduwa da kuma yadda take da haɗari kuma ba mu damu da ita ba".
Dokta Tom Frieden, wanda a dā shi ne shugaban Hukumar Kula da Cututtuka ta Amirka, ya ce wannan cuta "ba a yi tsammani ba".
A wata sanarwa da CNN ta wallafa a ranar Talata, ya ce, "ban da cutar ta HIV, babu wata cuta da ta kai hari a cikin tsarin da aka zaɓa na yin amfani da kwayoyin cutar tun lokacin da ta fara har zuwa lokacin da ta bazu a duniya".
Ghebreyesus ya yi irin wannan kalaman, yana mai cewa "ba mu taɓa ganin cutar coronavirus ta shafi duniya ba".
Ya daɗa cewa: "Babu wata matsala da za a iya magance ta a dukan duniya".
Wani sabon yanayi na rikicin duniya ya zo ne bayan da hukumar WHO ta yanke shawarar a watan Janairu ta bayyana barkewar cutar a matsayin matsalar lafiyar jama'a da ta shafi duniya.
