Hukumar ta WHO ta gano bambanci tsakanin barkewar cutar SARS a shekara ta 2002 zuwa 2004, lokacin da aka tilasta wa shugabannin kasar Sin su yi shiru game da abin da ya hana su gudanar da ayyukan rigakafi da yaki da cutar, da kuma matsalar da ke faruwa a yanzu yayin da gwamnatin tsakiya "tana ba da umarni ga jama'a koyaushe su guji yin rikici a shirye-shiryen hutun Sabuwar Shekara ta Lunar".
A ranar 23 ga Janairu, a cikin martani ga shawarar da jami'an gwamnati suka yanke na dakatar da zirga-zirga zuwa Wuhan, mai gabatar da jawabi ga WHO Gauden Galea ya ce ko da yake WHO ba ta yanke shawarar , yana da kyau  kuma yana nuna sadaukarwa ga yaki da cutar a yankin da ya fi fama da cutar  kuma ya bayyana ta a matsayin  ba a taɓa gani ba a tarihin kiwon lafiya . A ranar 30 ga Janairu, bayan an tabbatar da cewa ana yin jigilar mutane a waje da China kuma yawan cutar ta tashi a wasu ƙasashe, WHO ta bayyana cewa cutar ta zama Bala'i na Duniya wanda ake buƙatar kulawa da gaggawa (Public Health Emergency of International Concern (PHEIC), wanda aka gano a cikin rahoton 2009 cewa cutar ta tashi a matsayin babbar cuta.
Shugaban hukumar WHO, Tedros Adhanom, ya ce, "Halin da ya sa ake amfani da maganin PHEIC shi ne, ya sa ake fama da matsalar rashin lafiya a dukan duniya, musamman a ƙasashe masu karamin arziki.
A cikin martani ga dokar hana zirga-zirga, Tedros ya ce "babu dalilin da ya sa za a hana zirga-zirga da kasuwanci a dukan duniya" kuma "WHO ba ta goyon bayan rage zirga-zirga da zirga-zirga".
A ranar 5 ga Fabrairu, Hukumar Kula da Al'adu ta bukaci mutane a dukan duniya su ba da dala miliyan 675 don tallafa wa shirye-shiryen da ake yi a ƙasashe masu fama da cutar, kuma ta ce wajibi ne a ba da taimako da gaggawa ga ƙasashen da "ba su da tsarin gano waɗanda suka kamu da cutar, idan akwai wani yanayi".
Tedros ya kuma bayyana cewa "ƙarfinmu ya yi daidai da inda muka fi rauni" kuma ya yi kira ga mutane a duk duniya "su shuka yau ko su biya ƙarin a nan gaba". A ranar 11 ga Fabrairu, WHO a taron manema labarai ta sanar da COVID-19 a matsayin sunan cutar.
A ranar, Tedros ya bayyana cewa Sakataren Majalisar Dinkin Duniya António Guterres ya amince da ba da "dukan ƙarfin Majalisar Dinkin Duniya wajen yaki da cututtuka".
