Gwamnatin Donald Trump a Amurka ta kira coronavirus "Cutar Sin" ko "Cutar Wuhan" ta ce "nasara ta China ta haifar da cutar ta zama matsalar duniya", wanda wasu suka yi ta yi wa ba'a a matsayin nuna wariyar launin fata "saboda gazawar gwamnatinsa wajen yaki da cutar".
