Yin wanka kafin a yi magani ko kuma a yi magani zai iya rage yaduwar cututtuka.
Babban manufar maganin wanke hannu shi ne kashe ƙwayoyin cuta (bacteria, ƙwayoyin cuta, ko wasu ƙwayoyin cuta masu cutarwa) da kuma kawar da magunguna da za su iya haifar da cutar ko cutar.
