Ana yin su ne da isopropyl alcohol ko ethanol, wanda aka yi amfani da shi a matsayin mai ƙonewa kamar Carbomer (polymer na acrylic acid) don yin amfani da shi a matsayin mai ƙonewa, ko kuma a yi amfani da humectant kamar glycerin don yin amfani da shi a matsayin mai narkewa, ko kuma a yi amfani da shi don sauƙaƙa rayuwar masu amfani da shi da kuma rage yawan shan giya.
Ƙara hydrogen-peroxide a cikin ruwan sama yana ƙara ƙwayoyin cuta. Masu tsabtace hannu da suka ƙunshi giya da yawa fiye da kashi 60 zuwa 95% suna kashe ƙwayoyin cuta.
